		<title>06EMPLOYMENT</title>
		<content> DUE TO THE COMPARATIVELY SMALL SIZE OF
 THE FARMS IN THIS AREA,LITTLE OUTSIDE 
 LABOUR IS REQUIRED BUT A              
 'PICK-YOUR-OWN' ENTERPRISE EMPLOYS    
 CASUAL LABOUR IN THE SUMMER.          
 THERE IS LITTLE UNEMPLOYMENT AS A     
 NUMBER OF PERSONS ARE SELF-EMPLOYED AS
 BUILDERS,LORRY DRIVERS AND MECHANICS. 
 MANY WIVES WORK PART-TIME AND         
 ABERGAVENNY AND DISTRICT PROVIDES     
 EMPLOYMENT FOR THE LOCAL TEACHERS,SHOP
 ASSISTANTS,ENGINEERS,CLERICAL AND     
 HOSPITAL STAFF.                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
